{"tid":834041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴爾(DELL)傳晤投行 研以傳統方式招股上市","createTime":"2018-09-24T02:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T02:39:59.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"055012c84e7d0d54a75fb8f298f893222d54e23c","tid":834041,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:39:59.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》引述消息人士稱，戴爾科技(Dell Technologies)正研究以傳統方式上市，而不是以收購方式上市的可能性，因為有投資者不滿後者。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指出，該間美國電腦與科技巨擘將於本周接見多間投資銀行，確定承銷團名單。因此，該公司取消了原定本周為收購上市安排而進行的巡迴推介活動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1951650/%E6%88%B4%E7%88%BE%E5%82%B3%E6%99%A4%E6%8A%95%E8%A1%8C+%E7%A0%94%E4%BB%A5%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E6%8B%9B%E8%82%A1%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1951650%2F%25E6%2588%25B4%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%2599%25A4%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A1%258C%2B%25E7%25A0%2594%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2582%25A1%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%2582&d=9V0snLNjGsSXGZAvKmetov9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b2af2890\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1951650/%E6%88%B4%E7%88%BE%E5%82%B3%E6%99%A4%E6%8A%95%E8%A1%8C+%E7%A0%94%E4%BB%A5%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E6%8B%9B%E8%82%A1%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82</a>"}]}